# HTML / UI Rules

## Page Structure (every tool page)
1. `<head>` — Tailwind CDN → `css/app.css` → page-specific `<style>` (minimal)
2. `<header>` — lang-switcher + back link + badge + `<h1>` + subtitle
3. Snake stage — `#snakeCanvas`, `#snakeChomp`, `#snakeCaption`
4. Focus-bar or jump-nav (auto-generated)
5. `<section id="..." class="tool-page-section">` for each tool
6. Scripts: tool JS → `snake-mascot.js` → `snake-tools.js` → `i18n.js` → focus-mode IIFE

## Tool Section Template
```html
<section id="tool-slug" class="tool-page-section">
  <div class="tps-header">
    <span class="tps-icon">🔧</span>
    <div>
      <h2 class="tps-title" data-i18n="cat.slug.name">Title</h2>
      <p class="tps-desc" data-i18n="cat.slug.desc">Description.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tps-body">
    <!-- inputs + button + result -->
  </div>
</section>
```

## Input Rules
- ✅ `<input class="input-field" type="text" />`
- ✅ `<select class="input-field">`
- ✅ `<textarea class="input-field">`
- ❌ Never bare `<input>` without `class="input-field"`

## i18n on HTML
- Text: `data-i18n="key"` on the element
- Placeholder: `data-i18n-ph="key"` on input
- Directory links (index.html): both `.dir-item-name` and `.dir-item-desc` need `data-i18n`
